## getIndexExports() function

Returns the files or directories exported by the given `index.ts` file.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare function getIndexExports(index: string): string[];
```

## Parameters

|  Parameter | Type | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  index | string | The <code>index.ts</code> file to analyze. |

<b>Returns:</b>

A string Array containing a relative path to the exported files or directories.
